WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(Default) {
color: #ffffffff;
font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
font-size: 020px;
text-shadow: #000000ff -2px 0px 2px, #000000ff 0px 2px 2px, #000000ff 0px -2px 2px, #000000ff 2px 0px 2px;
background-color: #00000000;
}

c0000000
00:00:00.540 --> 00:00:01.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A green smoothie...</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:01.710 --> 00:00:03.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Excuse me...
-...a banana juice.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:03.300 --> 00:00:04.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-And a fresh strawberry...
-...could I have one fresh...</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:04.460 --> 00:00:06.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-...strawberry shake, and also.
-...shake would be nice!</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:06.220 --> 00:00:07.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Oh, I know!
-[ISKA] Let's see.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:07.550 --> 00:00:10.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOGETHER] Melon soda
with special coconut ice cream,</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:10.470 --> 00:00:11.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>topped with fresh whipped cream</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:11.850 --> 00:00:13.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and a swirl
of the enderflower syrup.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:13.930 --> 00:00:16.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, oh?</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:16.390 --> 00:00:17.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ahh?</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:19.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:19.390 --> 00:00:20.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-It's you.
-Hold on.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:24.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, my gosh, Alice?</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:24.110 --> 00:00:26.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska!
What are you doing here?</b></Default>

c0000014
00:01:57.490 --> 00:01:59.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing here,
Imperial soldier?</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Uh, who're you?
-[annoyed sigh]</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:02.080 --> 00:02:03.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does this ring a bell?</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:03.460 --> 00:02:04.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Rin!</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:06.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What brings you
to the Sovereignty?</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:09.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, it's funny
you should ask me.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:09.630 --> 00:02:12.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Of course, the man
can also pull off glasses.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:12.550 --> 00:02:15.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He looks so sophisticated.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Focus up, lady!</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:17.100 --> 00:02:18.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this for the Empire?</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:18.680 --> 00:02:21.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'Cause if it is,
I have to stop you.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:24.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, no, no, it's not like
that at all, I promise!</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:25.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE SERVER 202A]
Order for one melon soda</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:25.860 --> 00:02:27.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and one strawberry shake
is ready!</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:27.820 --> 00:02:28.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that's me.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:29.070 --> 00:02:31.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, be careful
not to drop it.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:31.110 --> 00:02:32.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Yeah, I'll do my best, thanks.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:32.900 --> 00:02:34.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen, this thing,
it's not a mission!</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:34.820 --> 00:02:36.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came here
against my will, okay?</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:36.950 --> 00:02:40.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I, uh, well...sort of...</b></Default>

c0000034
00:02:40.200 --> 00:02:41.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000035
00:02:41.450 --> 00:02:43.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What am I missing, then?</b></Default>

c0000036
00:02:43.210 --> 00:02:45.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can fill me in outside,
let's go.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:02:45.710 --> 00:02:47.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WARVICK] Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:02:47.210 --> 00:02:50.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're glad you're here,
thank you for coming.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:02:50.380 --> 00:02:52.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kisasage and Warvick!</b></Default>

c0000040
00:02:52.880 --> 00:02:54.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is Sisbell's
security detail.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:02:54.970 --> 00:02:57.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This young man, who is he?</b></Default>

c0000042
00:02:57.260 --> 00:03:00.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, he's, um... I was about
to give him some directions!</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:00.470 --> 00:03:02.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said this place
is like a maze,</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:02.140 --> 00:03:04.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I was trying
to help him find the exit.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:04.430 --> 00:03:06.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Now, off you go, sir!</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:06.350 --> 00:03:07.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Yeah, okay.
-[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:12.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] We'll regroup
at 9:00 p.m. sharp.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:14.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be ready to move out by then.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:14.320 --> 00:03:15.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Yes, ma'am, as you wish!
-Yes, ma'am, as you wish!</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:15.820 --> 00:03:17.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[slurps]
-[ALICE] Rin.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:18.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're looking for the soldier?</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:18.700 --> 00:03:20.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's headed
toward exit eight now.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:20.580 --> 00:03:22.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your drink, My Lady.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:22.290 --> 00:03:23.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Based on the stuff he ordered,</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:23.910 --> 00:03:26.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd say he's traveling
with at least one other person.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:26.500 --> 00:03:29.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Likely
a soldier from the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:29.380 --> 00:03:32.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That Captain Mismis.
You think it's her?</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:32.590 --> 00:03:33.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's very possible.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:35.220 --> 00:03:37.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whether it is or not,
we can't allow the Empire</b></Default>

c0000060
00:03:37.890 --> 00:03:39.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to infiltrate the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:42.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Over there...it's him.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:03:43.020 --> 00:03:44.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's a fool.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:03:44.100 --> 00:03:46.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How dare he hide
in plain sight!</b></Default>

c0000064
00:03:46.440 --> 00:03:48.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, that is rather strange.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:50.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why didn't he flee?</b></Default>

c0000066
00:03:50.110 --> 00:03:52.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Do you think he might
be waiting for someone?</b></Default>

c0000067
00:03:52.730 --> 00:03:53.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:03:53.820 --> 00:03:55.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slurps]</b></Default>

c0000069
00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:57.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What?
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000070
00:03:59.070 --> 00:04:00.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
It's Sisbell?</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:00.530 --> 00:04:02.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you for getting me
that drink!</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:02.370 --> 00:04:03.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry I made you wait.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:03.700 --> 00:04:06.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We need to leave, Sisbell.
Let's go!</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:06.160 --> 00:04:07.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah?!</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:07.250 --> 00:04:08.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean,
"we need to leave?"</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:08.920 --> 00:04:10.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you in such a hurry?</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:10.710 --> 00:04:12.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Hang on, Iska, wait for me!</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:12.880 --> 00:04:14.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She kept her
whereabouts a secret,</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:14.670 --> 00:04:16.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so it seems rational to assume</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:16.260 --> 00:04:18.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she has a connection
with the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:18.300 --> 00:04:20.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
But she's not incognito?</b></Default>

c0000082
00:04:20.340 --> 00:04:23.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] All right, sister.
What the hell are you up to?</b></Default>

c0000083
00:04:23.220 --> 00:04:24.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000084
00:04:26.890 --> 00:04:28.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Okay, why am I so irritated?</b></Default>

c0000085
00:04:29.020 --> 00:04:30.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not following them
because I'm jealous,</b></Default>

c0000086
00:04:30.770 --> 00:04:32.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it simply must be done!</b></Default>

c0000087
00:04:32.730 --> 00:04:33.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at them!</b></Default>

c0000088
00:04:33.980 --> 00:04:36.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Lady Sisbell took the drink!</b></Default>

c0000089
00:04:36.440 --> 00:04:38.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have eyes, Rin.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:04:38.700 --> 00:04:40.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Are you serious?</b></Default>

c0000091
00:04:40.110 --> 00:04:41.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's like
she's actually enjoying this!</b></Default>

c0000092
00:04:42.070 --> 00:04:44.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Lady Alice!
-What is it, now?</b></Default>

c0000093
00:04:44.490 --> 00:04:46.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Their shoulders.
They're about to touch!</b></Default>

c0000094
00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:48.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, they are like,
way too close together!</b></Default>

c0000095
00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:50.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is going on?</b></Default>

c0000096
00:04:50.210 --> 00:04:52.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That man's
an Imperial soldier, sis!</b></Default>

c0000097
00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:54.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My Lady, quick,
it's getting worse!</b></Default>

c0000098
00:04:54.540 --> 00:04:57.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Lady Sisbell's wrapping
her arm around his!</b></Default>

c0000099
00:04:57.340 --> 00:04:58.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[soft gasp]
-Hang on a sec!</b></Default>

c0000100
00:04:59.010 --> 00:05:00.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sister, how can you not see?</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:01.010 --> 00:05:02.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska's uncomfortable.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:02.550 --> 00:05:03.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:04.060 --> 00:05:05.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:06.850 --> 00:05:08.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:08.640 --> 00:05:10.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[heart pounding]</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:16.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice?</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:16.730 --> 00:05:18.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My goodness,
look at your poor face!</b></Default>

c0000108
00:05:18.490 --> 00:05:20.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Your cheeks
are incredibly flushed!</b></Default>

c0000109
00:05:20.200 --> 00:05:22.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, they are,
this is a serious matter, okay?</b></Default>

c0000110
00:05:22.570 --> 00:05:24.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would she
be doing this to me?</b></Default>

c0000111
00:05:24.700 --> 00:05:26.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska's mine!</b></Default>

c0000112
00:05:26.330 --> 00:05:28.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look, she's making moves again!</b></Default>

c0000113
00:05:28.750 --> 00:05:30.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:05:30.250 --> 00:05:31.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000115
00:05:31.500 --> 00:05:32.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000116
00:05:32.580 --> 00:05:33.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000117
00:05:33.710 --> 00:05:35.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000118
00:05:36.500 --> 00:05:40.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this utter lack of propriety
part of her disguise?</b></Default>

c0000119
00:05:40.170 --> 00:05:42.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never been so envious.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:05:42.340 --> 00:05:43.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pay that no mind!</b></Default>

c0000121
00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:46.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see?
Iska's in shock, too!</b></Default>

c0000122
00:05:46.350 --> 00:05:48.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, no, the horror!</b></Default>

c0000123
00:05:48.270 --> 00:05:51.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[deep breath]</b></Default>

c0000124
00:05:51.100 --> 00:05:53.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
No, Sisbell, you can't!</b></Default>

c0000125
00:05:53.810 --> 00:05:55.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't do it!</b></Default>

c0000126
00:05:55.690 --> 00:05:56.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chomps]</b></Default>

c0000127
00:05:56.770 --> 00:06:00.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[growls]
You want a war, you'll get one.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:00.280 --> 00:06:02.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, that's a little rash.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:02.700 --> 00:06:06.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, our greatest threat
wasn't the Empire, after all.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:06.660 --> 00:06:07.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
I'm sorry?</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:10.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll turn her into an ice
sculpture and sell her off.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:10.660 --> 00:06:12.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That traitor will fetch
a high price.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:15.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's your sister,
calm yourself!</b></Default>

c0000134
00:06:15.250 --> 00:06:17.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Let go of me, Rin!
-I shan't, M'Lady!</b></Default>

c0000135
00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:18.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mother will understand!</b></Default>

c0000136
00:06:19.010 --> 00:06:21.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This duel was as inevitable
as fate itself!</b></Default>

c0000137
00:06:21.380 --> 00:06:23.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There will not be any duels!</b></Default>

c0000138
00:06:24.430 --> 00:06:26.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh!
I guess you're right.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:06:26.850 --> 00:06:28.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least, the cream
wasn't on his lips,</b></Default>

c0000140
00:06:28.810 --> 00:06:30.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was only his cheek.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:06:30.100 --> 00:06:31.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay?</b></Default>

c0000142
00:06:31.230 --> 00:06:33.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice...
with your permission,</b></Default>

c0000143
00:06:33.600 --> 00:06:35.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like to handle
this matter myself.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:06:36.980 --> 00:06:40.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh, good Lord, I've never seen
the princess so flustered!</b></Default>

c0000145
00:06:40.150 --> 00:06:41.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's gotten into her?</b></Default>

c0000146
00:06:41.400 --> 00:06:42.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This was all
supposed to be over</b></Default>

c0000147
00:06:42.780 --> 00:06:44.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when Lady Sisbell
was back in our hands!</b></Default>

c0000148
00:06:45.030 --> 00:06:47.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shouldn't have to be
playing mediator right now!</b></Default>

c0000149
00:06:47.570 --> 00:06:49.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Damn Imperial swordsman!</b></Default>

c0000150
00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:50.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is all your fault!</b></Default>

c0000151
00:06:50.490 --> 00:06:52.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-It's you!
-Don't make a scene.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:06:52.750 --> 00:06:55.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Especially you, terrorist!</b></Default>

c0000153
00:06:55.170 --> 00:06:57.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Lady Sisbell,
we've been looking for you!</b></Default>

c0000154
00:06:57.710 --> 00:06:59.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not in your
usual clothes.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:06:59.790 --> 00:07:02.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Why?
-No time for that.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:07:02.090 --> 00:07:04.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Masked Lord suspects you
of treason.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:07:04.550 --> 00:07:05.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000158
00:07:05.630 --> 00:07:07.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have been sent
on a mission by the Queen.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:07:07.970 --> 00:07:11.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your sister and I
are here to protect you.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:07:11.180 --> 00:07:13.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't believe
I requested protection.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:07:13.850 --> 00:07:16.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could you relay
that message to Alice?</b></Default>

c0000162
00:07:16.230 --> 00:07:18.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I just have
one question for you.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:20.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're gonna ask
why I'm here, aren't you?</b></Default>

c0000164
00:07:20.190 --> 00:07:21.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-It's fine.
-Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:07:21.860 --> 00:07:24.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Truth is, I'm really
doing this for my boss.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:07:24.860 --> 00:07:28.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[SISBELL] Iska?
-We need to be honest, okay?</b></Default>

c0000167
00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:31.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we stay quiet, we'll make
enemies of both factions.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:07:31.200 --> 00:07:32.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you insist.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:07:32.740 --> 00:07:34.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'll be the one
to explain it.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:07:34.450 --> 00:07:36.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[CROWD]
Ah!</b></Default>

c0000171
00:07:36.290 --> 00:07:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000172
00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:39.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah?</b></Default>

c0000173
00:07:39.420 --> 00:07:41.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chomps]</b></Default>

c0000174
00:07:41.540 --> 00:07:42.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dee-lish.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:07:43.010 --> 00:07:46.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ALL] Ah!
-And I thought we were friends.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:07:46.260 --> 00:07:48.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been ages since the two
of us were in the same room,</b></Default>

c0000177
00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:49.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>yet, here we are.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:07:49.800 --> 00:07:52.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] First thing he does
is shove this in my face.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:07:54.140 --> 00:07:55.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[paper crinkling]</b></Default>

c0000180
00:07:55.520 --> 00:07:57.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000181
00:07:57.980 --> 00:08:00.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Emperor Yunmelngin,
you monster.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:08:02.110 --> 00:08:03.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What the hell's
going on with you?</b></Default>

c0000183
00:08:06.700 --> 00:08:08.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ISKA] We're back.
-[MISMIS] Welcome back!</b></Default>

c0000184
00:08:08.950 --> 00:08:10.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, what happened to her?</b></Default>

c0000185
00:08:10.780 --> 00:08:12.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Intro to espionage
must have worn her out.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:08:13.990 --> 00:08:16.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Jhin, can I ask you
to hold down the fort again?</b></Default>

c0000187
00:08:16.580 --> 00:08:18.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just keep it under an hour.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:08:18.710 --> 00:08:19.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Got it.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:22.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see you came alone,
as promised.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:08:22.460 --> 00:08:23.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Where's Lady Sisbell?</b></Default>

c0000192
00:08:25.300 --> 00:08:27.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's sleeping soundly.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:08:27.300 --> 00:08:30.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think someone wore her out
with the interrogation.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:08:30.140 --> 00:08:32.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]
She made her choice.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:08:32.300 --> 00:08:34.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would argue that
she only has herself to blame.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:08:34.930 --> 00:08:37.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't believe
she enlisted the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:08:37.310 --> 00:08:39.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the public finds out,
they'll riot.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:08:39.690 --> 00:08:42.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Well,
we didn't ask for any of this.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:08:42.150 --> 00:08:43.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'd rather get
our compensation now</b></Default>

c0000200
00:08:43.980 --> 00:08:45.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and immediately
leave the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:08:46.030 --> 00:08:49.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Those terms are strictly
between you and Lady Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:08:49.160 --> 00:08:51.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It will be a huge problem
if this comes to light,</b></Default>

c0000203
00:08:51.490 --> 00:08:54.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and if that happens...
you're all on your own.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:08:54.620 --> 00:08:58.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The royal family will have no
choice but to feign ignorance.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:08:58.160 --> 00:09:00.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They'll just turn
a blind eye, huh?</b></Default>

c0000206
00:09:00.170 --> 00:09:01.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Afraid so.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:09:01.500 --> 00:09:03.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't have believed
she had an Imperial soldier</b></Default>

c0000208
00:09:03.630 --> 00:09:04.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as a guard.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:06.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not until I saw you.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:09:07.170 --> 00:09:08.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000211
00:09:08.590 --> 00:09:10.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
However, Lady Alice requested</b></Default>

c0000212
00:09:10.930 --> 00:09:12.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to hear the story
directly from you.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:09:13.050 --> 00:09:14.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000214
00:09:14.140 --> 00:09:15.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
You're going in by yourself.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:09:16.060 --> 00:09:17.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What about you?
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000216
00:09:17.930 --> 00:09:19.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hurry up and go in.
-Ow!</b></Default>

c0000217
00:09:19.560 --> 00:09:21.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll likely be interrogated
or tortured!</b></Default>

c0000218
00:09:21.770 --> 00:09:24.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not exactly
talking me into it.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:09:24.520 --> 00:09:27.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For some reason, her emotions
have been all over the place.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:09:27.900 --> 00:09:29.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Weird, I wonder why?</b></Default>

c0000221
00:09:29.690 --> 00:09:30.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
No idea.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:09:30.950 --> 00:09:32.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I know for sure is,
someone's going</b></Default>

c0000223
00:09:32.740 --> 00:09:34.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to have to be sacrificed
to her rage.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:09:34.820 --> 00:09:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I'm not volunteering.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:09:36.540 --> 00:09:38.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, well, I'm not either!</b></Default>

c0000226
00:09:38.160 --> 00:09:41.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Too bad!
-[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000227
00:09:41.460 --> 00:09:43.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000228
00:09:44.380 --> 00:09:46.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000229
00:09:46.630 --> 00:09:48.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000230
00:09:50.590 --> 00:09:51.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:53.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, hi?</b></Default>

c0000232
00:09:53.260 --> 00:09:55.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen, Rin brought me here
to talk to you because...</b></Default>

c0000233
00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:58.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she said you wanted info,
and that you wanted it from me?</b></Default>

c0000234
00:09:58.850 --> 00:10:00.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ALICE] I don't care.
-[ISKA] Hm?</b></Default>

c0000235
00:10:03.350 --> 00:10:05.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not
what you're here for.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:10:05.520 --> 00:10:07.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000237
00:10:07.730 --> 00:10:10.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me...why, Iska?</b></Default>

c0000238
00:10:11.450 --> 00:10:13.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just what is the meaning
of all of this?</b></Default>

c0000239
00:10:13.570 --> 00:10:16.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd answer you,
but, I don't actually know</b></Default>

c0000240
00:10:16.450 --> 00:10:17.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what you're asking me.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:10:19.370 --> 00:10:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were walking
around with her.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:10:21.700 --> 00:10:24.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ISKA] With Sisbell?
-Mm-hm.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:10:24.380 --> 00:10:26.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't think I saw you?</b></Default>

c0000244
00:10:26.170 --> 00:10:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, yeah.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:10:27.840 --> 00:10:29.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were doing
some recon back there.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:10:29.880 --> 00:10:32.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Making sure Masked Lord
hadn't followed us.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:35.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What we're doing is
unacceptable to both nations.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:10:35.340 --> 00:10:36.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I know it's wrong.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:10:36.760 --> 00:10:38.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I-Is that why
you're so upset right now?</b></Default>

c0000250
00:10:39.810 --> 00:10:41.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:10:41.680 --> 00:10:43.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, it's just...</b></Default>

c0000252
00:10:43.730 --> 00:10:45.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice, look...</b></Default>

c0000253
00:10:45.270 --> 00:10:47.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't intend
to hurt your feelings.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:49.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I won't know
what I did until you tell me.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:10:51.490 --> 00:10:53.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
You were walking together.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:10:53.700 --> 00:10:54.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pardon?</b></Default>

c0000257
00:10:54.780 --> 00:10:57.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Just, strutting
around, holding hands...</b></Default>

c0000258
00:10:57.410 --> 00:10:59.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you came here without me!</b></Default>

c0000259
00:10:59.780 --> 00:11:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but, I'm her bodyguard.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:11:01.700 --> 00:11:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So?</b></Default>

c0000261
00:11:02.580 --> 00:11:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should really be more
sensitive to these things!</b></Default>

c0000262
00:11:05.830 --> 00:11:08.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-It's just, Sisbell gets...</b></Default>

c0000263
00:11:10.130 --> 00:11:11.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all the fun!</b></Default>

c0000264
00:11:11.210 --> 00:11:12.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No fair!</b></Default>

c0000265
00:11:12.460 --> 00:11:13.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000266
00:11:13.970 --> 00:11:15.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000267
00:11:15.260 --> 00:11:17.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's betrayal,
plain and simple!</b></Default>

c0000268
00:11:17.300 --> 00:11:18.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Wait, a betrayal of what?</b></Default>

c0000269
00:11:18.890 --> 00:11:20.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
You promised you'd be my rival!</b></Default>

c0000270
00:11:20.970 --> 00:11:23.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you're letting her
boss you around!</b></Default>

c0000271
00:11:23.270 --> 00:11:25.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't exactly
call this a betrayal!</b></Default>

c0000272
00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:27.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our lives are kinda
on the line, you know!</b></Default>

c0000273
00:11:28.020 --> 00:11:30.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, well, I refuse
to accept that stance.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:11:30.820 --> 00:11:31.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How about this?</b></Default>

c0000275
00:11:32.030 --> 00:11:34.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we cease
our operation right away,</b></Default>

c0000276
00:11:34.280 --> 00:11:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would you give us
a few nebula bandages?</b></Default>

c0000277
00:11:36.780 --> 00:11:39.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]
No, I would never do that!</b></Default>

c0000278
00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:42.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? You think I would just
help out our enemies?</b></Default>

c0000279
00:11:42.410 --> 00:11:44.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that case,
you leave us no choice.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:11:44.290 --> 00:11:46.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000281
00:11:46.500 --> 00:11:48.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, childish protest
won't change things.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:11:50.130 --> 00:11:52.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning sigh]
This ordeal enrages me.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:11:52.710 --> 00:11:54.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you don't even care.</b></Default>

c0000284
00:11:54.420 --> 00:11:56.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, it'd be weird if I did.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:11:56.590 --> 00:11:57.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're enemies, after all.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:11:58.010 --> 00:12:00.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, maybe that's why
I'm cooling down.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:12:00.550 --> 00:12:01.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or it could be your face.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:12:02.010 --> 00:12:03.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm feeling better regardless.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:05.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And just to be clear...</b></Default>

c0000290
00:12:06.060 --> 00:12:08.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]
...I'm not angry with you.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:12:08.650 --> 00:12:11.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-At least, not right now.
-[ISKA] You're not?</b></Default>

c0000292
00:12:11.270 --> 00:12:13.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, you're not angry
with Sisbell either, right?</b></Default>

c0000293
00:12:13.530 --> 00:12:15.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, I'm mad at her!</b></Default>

c0000294
00:12:15.230 --> 00:12:17.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's the one
I'm super pissed off at!</b></Default>

c0000295
00:12:17.530 --> 00:12:19.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I see.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:12:19.110 --> 00:12:20.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you gonna do, then?</b></Default>

c0000297
00:12:20.740 --> 00:12:22.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Great question.
-Aah?</b></Default>

c0000298
00:12:22.700 --> 00:12:23.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
You were summoned here today</b></Default>

c0000299
00:12:24.040 --> 00:12:25.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for your official testimony.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:12:25.910 --> 00:12:29.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As the second-ranking princess
of the Nebulis Sovereignty,</b></Default>

c0000301
00:12:29.170 --> 00:12:31.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm allowed to prosecute
the lower-ranked princesses.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:34.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They allow that sort of thing?</b></Default>

c0000303
00:12:34.800 --> 00:12:37.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah, I'll form a committee
when we get back to the palace.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:12:37.550 --> 00:12:39.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
You're taking this too far!</b></Default>

c0000305
00:12:39.590 --> 00:12:42.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's my duty to find out
what she did to you.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:12:42.510 --> 00:12:44.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And as your one and only rival,</b></Default>

c0000307
00:12:44.640 --> 00:12:47.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do believe
I have the right to know.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:12:47.230 --> 00:12:48.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
What's with the glasses?</b></Default>

c0000309
00:12:49.020 --> 00:12:51.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
They're for the reenactment.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:12:52.520 --> 00:12:54.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000311
00:12:56.820 --> 00:12:58.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice!, what is this?</b></Default>

c0000312
00:12:59.030 --> 00:13:01.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was the witness
holding onto her hand?</b></Default>

c0000313
00:13:02.160 --> 00:13:03.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Like this.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:13:03.410 --> 00:13:05.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[whimpering]
-[ALICE] Hey! Stay right here!</b></Default>

c0000315
00:13:05.330 --> 00:13:07.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-Is this what she was doing?</b></Default>

c0000316
00:13:08.040 --> 00:13:09.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
For accuracy.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:13:09.540 --> 00:13:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] You know the answer,
you saw it happen!</b></Default>

c0000318
00:13:11.830 --> 00:13:14.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, but I must
experience it to understand!</b></Default>

c0000319
00:13:15.040 --> 00:13:16.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, where were we?</b></Default>

c0000320
00:13:16.920 --> 00:13:19.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yes, that's right.
Your hand is quite rough.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:13:19.680 --> 00:13:21.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
You're acting so weird!</b></Default>

c0000322
00:13:21.300 --> 00:13:23.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a real investigation!</b></Default>

c0000323
00:13:23.390 --> 00:13:25.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Look how scandalous this is!</b></Default>

c0000324
00:13:25.350 --> 00:13:26.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000325
00:13:26.430 --> 00:13:27.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
A princess of the Sovereignty,</b></Default>

c0000326
00:13:27.770 --> 00:13:30.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>locking arms with the enemy
in broad daylight.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:13:30.560 --> 00:13:33.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, much the same
as you're doing right now.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:13:33.360 --> 00:13:36.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just trying
to verify the facts here!</b></Default>

c0000329
00:13:36.190 --> 00:13:38.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With a case like this,
the smaller details matter,</b></Default>

c0000330
00:13:38.940 --> 00:13:41.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so the examination
has got to be thorough!</b></Default>

c0000331
00:13:41.740 --> 00:13:42.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Thorough," eh?</b></Default>

c0000332
00:13:42.950 --> 00:13:45.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Let's see...
if memory serves me,</b></Default>

c0000333
00:13:45.620 --> 00:13:46.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe you two were
a lot closer that day.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:13:47.080 --> 00:13:48.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait!</b></Default>

c0000335
00:13:48.160 --> 00:13:50.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-[ALICE] Yeah, like this.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:13:50.370 --> 00:13:51.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000337
00:13:52.040 --> 00:13:54.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, Alice,
you're acting strange!</b></Default>

c0000338
00:13:54.670 --> 00:13:57.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What are you doing?
-Being thorough, remember?</b></Default>

c0000339
00:13:59.550 --> 00:14:00.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's just not fair.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:14:00.880 --> 00:14:03.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Walking around, so sinfully.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:06.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it's so sinful,
then maybe you should let go.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:14:06.300 --> 00:14:08.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not that easy!</b></Default>

c0000343
00:14:08.100 --> 00:14:11.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000344
00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:15.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing now?</b></Default>

c0000345
00:14:15.900 --> 00:14:17.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
I-I dunno, I'm nervous!</b></Default>

c0000346
00:14:17.570 --> 00:14:19.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course,
my breathing is labored,</b></Default>

c0000347
00:14:19.150 --> 00:14:21.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being so close to my enemy.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:23.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Just let go of me, then!</b></Default>

c0000349
00:14:23.200 --> 00:14:25.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
But I don't wanna let go.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:14:25.740 --> 00:14:26.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Ah?
-No!</b></Default>

c0000351
00:14:26.990 --> 00:14:28.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've got the wrong idea!</b></Default>

c0000352
00:14:28.870 --> 00:14:31.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] It's not
like that, Iska, I just...</b></Default>

c0000353
00:14:31.910 --> 00:14:35.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was trying to understand
what Sisbell was feeling, okay?</b></Default>

c0000354
00:14:36.380 --> 00:14:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000355
00:14:40.760 --> 00:14:42.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000356
00:14:43.090 --> 00:14:44.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000357
00:14:50.350 --> 00:14:52.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...I was just thinking.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:14:52.680 --> 00:14:54.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[door slams open]
-I'm here!</b></Default>

c0000359
00:14:54.390 --> 00:14:57.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you all right, My Lady?</b></Default>

c0000360
00:14:57.150 --> 00:14:58.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
I couldn't stand it.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:14:58.360 --> 00:15:00.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's too dangerous
for you two to be alone!</b></Default>

c0000362
00:15:00.860 --> 00:15:03.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin, I was in the middle
of something!</b></Default>

c0000363
00:15:03.700 --> 00:15:05.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[RIN] And that was?
-Uh...</b></Default>

c0000364
00:15:05.950 --> 00:15:08.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Look at you.
-[ALICE] What is it?</b></Default>

c0000365
00:15:08.280 --> 00:15:10.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Your skin,
it's positively glowing.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:15:10.910 --> 00:15:12.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah?
You don't say.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:15:12.700 --> 00:15:14.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did something happen?</b></Default>

c0000368
00:15:14.750 --> 00:15:16.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?
No way!</b></Default>

c0000369
00:15:16.080 --> 00:15:18.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your cheeks
are as red as the sunset.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:15:18.250 --> 00:15:20.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, please,
you're just imagining things!</b></Default>

c0000371
00:15:20.710 --> 00:15:22.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Ma'am, if I may.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:15:22.340 --> 00:15:24.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't good,
you're burning up!</b></Default>

c0000373
00:15:24.220 --> 00:15:26.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must get some bed-rest
immediately, I insist!</b></Default>

c0000374
00:15:26.970 --> 00:15:29.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not true,
I'm perfectly fine.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:15:29.430 --> 00:15:30.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a monster!</b></Default>

c0000376
00:15:30.810 --> 00:15:33.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice clearly has a fever
and you've chosen to respond</b></Default>

c0000377
00:15:33.730 --> 00:15:35.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the weak cowardice
of inaction!</b></Default>

c0000378
00:15:35.430 --> 00:15:36.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've got it all wrong!</b></Default>

c0000379
00:15:36.810 --> 00:15:39.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Silence, villain, you have
two seconds to get out!</b></Default>

c0000380
00:15:39.230 --> 00:15:42.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You guys are the ones
who told me to come in here!</b></Default>

c0000381
00:15:43.230 --> 00:15:45.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000382
00:15:47.950 --> 00:15:50.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Oh, man, I can still
feel Alice's warmth.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:15:51.030 --> 00:15:52.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[running footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000384
00:15:52.290 --> 00:15:54.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not fair!</b></Default>

c0000385
00:15:54.080 --> 00:15:55.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They've got everything wrong!</b></Default>

c0000386
00:15:55.540 --> 00:15:57.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[running footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000387
00:15:57.920 --> 00:16:00.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR] I'm impressed.
Happy, even!</b></Default>

c0000388
00:16:01.170 --> 00:16:03.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't think
you had it in you.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:16:03.130 --> 00:16:05.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Calling for a fake
emergency conference.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:08.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All to keep the Zoa here,
so Alice has more time</b></Default>

c0000391
00:16:08.430 --> 00:16:09.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to find Sisbell?</b></Default>

c0000392
00:16:09.930 --> 00:16:13.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Abusing your sacred authority
for your own benefit.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:16:13.100 --> 00:16:14.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well!</b></Default>

c0000394
00:16:14.180 --> 00:16:16.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
My heart is racing.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:16:16.350 --> 00:16:17.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is how a queen should be!</b></Default>

c0000396
00:16:17.730 --> 00:16:18.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Elletear, dear.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:16:18.980 --> 00:16:21.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Refrain from making misleading
statements, please.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:16:21.570 --> 00:16:23.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
My apologies, Your Majesty!</b></Default>

c0000399
00:16:23.980 --> 00:16:26.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was simply making
small talk to pass the time!</b></Default>

c0000400
00:16:26.900 --> 00:16:28.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your Majesty, it's time to go.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:16:28.990 --> 00:16:30.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Right. Shall we?</b></Default>

c0000402
00:16:30.910 --> 00:16:32.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000403
00:16:37.250 --> 00:16:40.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)] House
of Lou, I bid thee farewell!</b></Default>

c0000404
00:16:40.710 --> 00:16:43.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000405
00:16:43.170 --> 00:16:46.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not today.
Legion of Divine Wind!</b></Default>

c0000406
00:16:46.590 --> 00:16:47.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000407
00:16:47.970 --> 00:16:49.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000408
00:16:49.300 --> 00:16:50.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is everyone all right?</b></Default>

c0000409
00:16:50.840 --> 00:16:51.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE SOLDIER 202A]
Yes.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:16:51.930 --> 00:16:53.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE SOLDIER 202A] We'll all
be okay, thanks to you.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:16:53.890 --> 00:16:55.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we must stop your bleeding!</b></Default>

c0000412
00:16:55.560 --> 00:16:57.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be fine, I assure you.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:16:57.480 --> 00:16:59.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My palms are red,
but it's only a bruise.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:16:59.980 --> 00:17:01.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was a very close call.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:17:02.860 --> 00:17:05.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were all lucky to be in your
presence when it happened.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:17:05.230 --> 00:17:06.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My Queen!</b></Default>

c0000417
00:17:06.400 --> 00:17:08.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE SOLDIER 202C]
Lady Elletear, what was that?</b></Default>

c0000418
00:17:08.320 --> 00:17:10.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone just made
an attempt on the crown.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:17:10.660 --> 00:17:12.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you see anyone
suspicious outside the door?</b></Default>

c0000420
00:17:13.030 --> 00:17:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE SOLDIER 202D]
No!</b></Default>

c0000421
00:17:14.030 --> 00:17:15.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE SOLDIER 202C]
We saw nothing worth reporting!</b></Default>

c0000422
00:17:15.580 --> 00:17:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your Majesty,
I can't say for sure,</b></Default>

c0000423
00:17:18.830 --> 00:17:21.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I think I heard a familiar
voice before the flames.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:17:21.630 --> 00:17:24.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a coincidence,
I think I heard it, too.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:17:24.590 --> 00:17:28.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, to me, it sounded
the same as Masked Lord.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:17:28.760 --> 00:17:31.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, dare I say,
I heard it, too.</b></Default>

c0000427
00:17:31.180 --> 00:17:32.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did, too.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:17:32.890 --> 00:17:34.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The conference is now canceled.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:17:34.810 --> 00:17:36.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
My Queen, what's this?</b></Default>

c0000430
00:17:36.640 --> 00:17:38.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The throne room's destroyed.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:17:38.350 --> 00:17:40.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't believe what I'm seeing
before the family meets.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:17:40.980 --> 00:17:43.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were all attacked just now.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:17:43.150 --> 00:17:44.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was the plot
of a ruthless traitor</b></Default>

c0000434
00:17:44.860 --> 00:17:47.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who had schemed
to assassinate me.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:17:47.360 --> 00:17:49.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?
Who was it?</b></Default>

c0000436
00:17:49.570 --> 00:17:51.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
By all accounts, it was you.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:17:52.070 --> 00:17:53.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did I hear you correctly?</b></Default>

c0000438
00:17:54.030 --> 00:17:56.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Help me understand
what you mean.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:17:56.200 --> 00:17:59.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can explain it yourself
on the witness stand.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:17:59.710 --> 00:18:02.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I see.
What an interesting twist.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:18:02.830 --> 00:18:05.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will interview each and every
member of the House of Zo--</b></Default>

c0000442
00:18:05.670 --> 00:18:07.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN] I implore you
to wait, Your Majesty.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:18:08.050 --> 00:18:10.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As the head of Hydra,
you know I always look forward</b></Default>

c0000444
00:18:10.550 --> 00:18:13.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to these conferences
of the Three Founding Families.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:18:13.300 --> 00:18:15.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it seems
there's been a disaster.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:18:15.800 --> 00:18:18.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Lord Talisman.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:18:18.430 --> 00:18:20.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
Before we make any decisions,</b></Default>

c0000448
00:18:20.310 --> 00:18:22.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it's important
we attend to these wounds.</b></Default>

c0000449
00:18:24.230 --> 00:18:26.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We cannot risk something
happening to you!</b></Default>

c0000450
00:18:26.480 --> 00:18:27.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Treat her! Right away!</b></Default>

c0000451
00:18:27.940 --> 00:18:28.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Sir!
-Sir!</b></Default>

c0000452
00:18:29.030 --> 00:18:32.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And who would you suggest
deal with the House of Zoa?</b></Default>

c0000453
00:18:32.700 --> 00:18:34.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Allow me to make things right.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:18:34.870 --> 00:18:35.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you?</b></Default>

c0000455
00:18:35.950 --> 00:18:37.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
If you have concerns,</b></Default>

c0000456
00:18:37.200 --> 00:18:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll make sure a recorder from
the House of Lou is present.</b></Default>

c0000457
00:18:39.950 --> 00:18:42.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And we'll continue to look for
the culprit at the same time.</b></Default>

c0000458
00:18:43.580 --> 00:18:45.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A serious incident like this
may not be the work</b></Default>

c0000459
00:18:45.790 --> 00:18:47.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of Masked Lord alone.</b></Default>

c0000460
00:18:47.500 --> 00:18:49.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's possible the House of Zoa
or outsiders</b></Default>

c0000461
00:18:49.760 --> 00:18:51.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>such as the Empire
are involved.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:18:52.880 --> 00:18:54.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vichyssoise, show yourself.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:18:54.680 --> 00:18:56.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000464
00:19:00.060 --> 00:19:01.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My Queen,</b></Default>

c0000465
00:19:01.350 --> 00:19:03.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd be honored to help you.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:19:03.890 --> 00:19:07.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR] I am also in favor
of Lord Talisman's proposal.</b></Default>

c0000467
00:19:07.480 --> 00:19:09.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:19:09.150 --> 00:19:10.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Your Majesty.</b></Default>

c0000469
00:19:10.520 --> 00:19:13.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This was an assassination
attempt on you.</b></Default>

c0000470
00:19:13.400 --> 00:19:15.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We must mobilize
all the royal families.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:19:15.820 --> 00:19:17.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For the Sovereignty!</b></Default>

c0000472
00:19:17.410 --> 00:19:18.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000473
00:19:19.030 --> 00:19:20.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Very well, then.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:19:20.370 --> 00:19:22.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lord Talisman, Vichyssoise,</b></Default>

c0000475
00:19:22.240 --> 00:19:23.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would you assist
our great house?</b></Default>

c0000476
00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:26.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We shall use our combined might
to resolve this</b></Default>

c0000477
00:19:26.460 --> 00:19:27.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and leave it behind.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:19:27.750 --> 00:19:29.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll make arrangements
right away.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:19:29.670 --> 00:19:32.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000480
00:19:32.340 --> 00:19:35.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is Masked Lord
capable of such treachery?</b></Default>

c0000481
00:19:35.800 --> 00:19:37.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] It seems the
only way to get through this</b></Default>

c0000482
00:19:37.510 --> 00:19:39.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is with Sisbell's help.</b></Default>

c0000483
00:19:39.470 --> 00:19:41.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She would be able
to identify the crime,</b></Default>

c0000484
00:19:41.260 --> 00:19:43.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and our true culprit.</b></Default>

c0000485
00:19:43.140 --> 00:19:44.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
I'm sure our enemies</b></Default>

c0000486
00:19:44.180 --> 00:19:45.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will come to the
same conclusion.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:19:46.020 --> 00:19:48.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And with that,
mark their next target.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:19:49.060 --> 00:19:50.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Make haste, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:19:50.360 --> 00:19:52.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bring Sisbell
back to the palace.</b></Default>

c0000490
00:19:52.940 --> 00:19:55.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1B] This is
quite an accomplishment, Risya.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:19:55.860 --> 00:19:57.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
Through Omen's research,</b></Default>

c0000492
00:19:57.200 --> 00:20:00.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we created artificial astral
crests for our soldiers.</b></Default>

c0000493
00:20:00.530 --> 00:20:02.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The trial was a success.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:20:02.330 --> 00:20:05.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Out of twelve attempted border
crossings, ten succeeded.</b></Default>

c0000495
00:20:05.620 --> 00:20:08.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA] To be honest, I was
terrified it might not work.</b></Default>

c0000496
00:20:08.750 --> 00:20:10.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
Worry not!</b></Default>

c0000497
00:20:10.130 --> 00:20:13.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One of the units made it to the
Sovereignty's Central Province.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:20:13.380 --> 00:20:15.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm honored to be recognized.</b></Default>

c0000499
00:20:15.210 --> 00:20:18.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But instead of a cheap bonus,
could I just have a vacation?</b></Default>

c0000500
00:20:18.890 --> 00:20:21.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A] You
will have to ask the Emperor.</b></Default>

c0000501
00:20:21.260 --> 00:20:24.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unfortunately, you are not
under our jurisdiction.</b></Default>

c0000502
00:20:24.890 --> 00:20:27.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why did I have a feeling
you'd tell me that?</b></Default>

c0000503
00:20:27.690 --> 00:20:30.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did any of them make it
into the Royal Palace?</b></Default>

c0000504
00:20:30.230 --> 00:20:32.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
I'm afraid not, no.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:20:32.110 --> 00:20:34.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
However, something interesting</b></Default>

c0000506
00:20:34.360 --> 00:20:36.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>occurred in the palace itself.</b></Default>

c0000507
00:20:36.280 --> 00:20:38.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
Yeah? First I've heard of it.</b></Default>

c0000508
00:20:38.820 --> 00:20:40.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1B] It
seems Queen Nebulis the 8th</b></Default>

c0000509
00:20:40.700 --> 00:20:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was attacked.</b></Default>

c0000510
00:20:41.950 --> 00:20:43.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just so we're on the same page,</b></Default>

c0000511
00:20:43.490 --> 00:20:45.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are you sure it wasn't
an Imperial attack?</b></Default>

c0000512
00:20:45.620 --> 00:20:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
Positive.</b></Default>

c0000513
00:20:46.700 --> 00:20:48.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are descendants
of the Founders</b></Default>

c0000514
00:20:48.410 --> 00:20:50.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that are unhappy
with the current Queen.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:20:50.710 --> 00:20:54.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That seems a little extreme
for just being "unhappy."</b></Default>

c0000516
00:20:54.250 --> 00:20:57.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could you simply tell me
what you're getting at, please?</b></Default>

c0000517
00:20:57.170 --> 00:20:58.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have someone
in the Sovereignty</b></Default>

c0000518
00:20:58.630 --> 00:21:01.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>helping the Empire, don't you?</b></Default>

c0000519
00:21:01.300 --> 00:21:03.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1B] As a
reward for your accomplishment,</b></Default>

c0000520
00:21:03.180 --> 00:21:04.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll divulge one thing to you.</b></Default>

c0000521
00:21:05.020 --> 00:21:06.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
We do have a contact</b></Default>

c0000522
00:21:06.390 --> 00:21:08.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the inside
who keeps in touch.</b></Default>

c0000523
00:21:08.350 --> 00:21:09.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
This person is a purebred</b></Default>

c0000524
00:21:09.810 --> 00:21:12.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the Sovereignty,
they go by Subject E.</b></Default>

c0000525
00:21:12.900 --> 00:21:14.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000526
00:21:14.440 --> 00:21:17.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently, the attack
has them a bit rattled.</b></Default>

c0000527
00:21:17.690 --> 00:21:19.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
Well, yeah.</b></Default>

c0000528
00:21:19.450 --> 00:21:21.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can see how a failed attempt
on the Queen's life</b></Default>

c0000529
00:21:21.780 --> 00:21:23.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would rattle
a monarchical nation.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:21:23.830 --> 00:21:24.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
We see this</b></Default>

c0000531
00:21:24.830 --> 00:21:27.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as a perfect opportunity.</b></Default>

c0000532
00:21:27.500 --> 00:21:29.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey! You miss me?</b></Default>

c0000533
00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Still alive, I see!</b></Default>

c0000534
00:21:31.880 --> 00:21:34.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
Saint Disciples, welcome!</b></Default>

c0000535
00:21:34.500 --> 00:21:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
We've called upon you</b></Default>

c0000536
00:21:35.710 --> 00:21:37.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to join the war effort.</b></Default>

c0000537
00:21:37.460 --> 00:21:39.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
Your mission is to capture</b></Default>

c0000538
00:21:39.220 --> 00:21:41.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Queen and the purebreds.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:21:41.090 --> 00:21:43.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you'd never ask!
Purebreds, eh?</b></Default>

c0000540
00:21:43.890 --> 00:21:46.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've always wanted
to see one with my own eyes!</b></Default>

c0000541
00:21:46.470 --> 00:21:48.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've always wanted you
to shut up.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:50.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your voice disturbs
the natural order.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:21:50.980 --> 00:21:52.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1B]
Spectacular.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:21:52.100 --> 00:21:53.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
We've never had so many</b></Default>

c0000545
00:21:53.350 --> 00:21:54.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>elite soldiers in one place.</b></Default>

c0000546
00:21:55.020 --> 00:21:57.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS] There are too many
cooks in the kitchen.</b></Default>

c0000547
00:21:57.280 --> 00:21:58.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can do this on my own.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:21:58.820 --> 00:22:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This plan will cost you
and I hope you can afford it.</b></Default>

c0000549
00:22:02.030 --> 00:22:04.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, great!
Looks like everyone's here.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:22:04.160 --> 00:22:06.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000551
00:22:06.490 --> 00:22:08.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000552
00:22:08.200 --> 00:22:10.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000553
00:22:10.830 --> 00:22:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should all the
Emperor's elite soldiers</b></Default>

c0000554
00:22:12.580 --> 00:22:14.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>be in the same place at once?</b></Default>

c0000555
00:22:14.170 --> 00:22:16.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This feels unnecessarily
risky to me.</b></Default>

c0000556
00:22:16.920 --> 00:22:19.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A] Again,
your concern is misplaced.</b></Default>

c0000557
00:22:19.710 --> 00:22:22.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We cleared this
with the Emperor in advance.</b></Default>

c0000558
00:22:22.800 --> 00:22:24.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are the
highest-ranking combatants</b></Default>

c0000559
00:22:24.550 --> 00:22:26.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Empire has to offer.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:22:26.720 --> 00:22:29.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I invite you to do your worst.</b></Default>

